column5: Heading down for some eyes on the weekend, not sure if i mist it in the regs, and wanted to make sure, wondering how many rods per man in Quinte? Thanks
2 rods east of the ferry and 1 rod west of the ferry.
Also, there's a 4 fish limit with only 1 being over 24"....
did you have any luck?...we didn't ...too early I guess
